<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 29 (Xinhua) -- It is the obligation of
software providers like Computer Associates International, Inc. (
CA) to offer top-quality products for customers in this Internet
era, the head of CA said in a speech today to students at Qinghua
University.
