<HEADLINE> Share Prices Edge Up Marginally on Singapore Stock  Market </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SINGAPORE, February 29 (Xinhua) -- Share prices ended mostly
flat on the Singapore Stock Market Tuesday as selling pressure
offset selective buying interest.
</P>
