<HEADLINE> Kenya Lifts Ban on Logging </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, February 29 (Xinhua) -- The Kenyan government has
lifted the ban on logging, according to Tuesday's Daily Nation
newspaper.
</P>
