<HEADLINE> CCB Supports Oil Development in West China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 29 (Xinhua) -- The China Construction Bank (
CCB) will give strong support to the development of oil in
northwestern China, with a bank-corporate cooperation agreement
signed here today between it's Xinjiang branch and the China New
Star Oil Corporation, which develops oil resources in the western
regions.
</P>
<P>
