always supported the state's key construction projects, especially
in the oil development sector. Today's agreement is a significant
step made in response to the state's newly-designed strategy of
developing the western regions.
</P>
<P>
So far the CCB has supplied loans of 970 million yuan to the
Northwestern Oil Bureau, with a total settled amount of 2.5
billion yuan, largely supporting its oil development in the
northwest.  
