<HEADLINE> 102 Kilograms of Marijuana Seized in Truck Crash in Albania </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, February 28 (Xinhua) -- A total of 102 kilograms of
marijuana were found in a truck following an accident near Patos
in Albania on Monday, police said.
</P>
<P>
The crash occurred at about 2 p.m.(1200GMT) near Patos, in the
northern part of Albania, when an Iveco truck ran into a bus,
police said.
</P>
<P>
Police arrived at the scene immediately and found the marijuana
in 55 packages concealed inside the truck.
</P>
<P>
An investigation is underway. Police are searching for the
driver who fled the scene after the crash. The plates on the truck
were reportedly false. 
</P>
