send its ambassador back to Vienna, Israeli Foreign Ministry said
Tuesday in a statement.
</P>
<P>
Haider, an outspoken xenophobe and sympathizer of the Nazis,
announced his stepping down as leader of the Freedom Party late
Monday night. (Israel-Austria-Haider)
</P>
<P>
- - - -
</P>
<P>
TEHRAN -- Iran's military court on Tuesday started open trial of
the policemen who were charged of attacking students in the Tehran
University dormitory last July.
</P>
<P>
